Quota:

    quota is a resource management mechanism that limits the amount of resources (such as CPU, memory, storage, or the number of objects) that can be consumed by pods,replicasts and others within a project


1) Create project p8

2) create Quota name my-quota
  
    pods: "3"
    cpu: 1
    memory: 1G


3) oc create quota --help  (get the command, modify it and create quota)

4) validate quota

  